channel.title: 317, Un-Nulling bottom left tab PI
channel.description:
How can i un-Null the bottom left tab?..
I know there is a way, if you guys say its 7, no its not 7 is where the clan chat is right now. ;o
Can someone please help Un-Null it!
[IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/34pyttg.png[/img]

item.title: 317, Un-Nulling bottom left tab PI
item.dc:creator: @Christmas_tree Christmas_tree
item.description:
@Christmas_tree wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:3, topic:478362”][quote author=Christmas_tree link=topic=596555.msg4200549#msg4200549 date=1358125956]
By un-null you mean what exactly?

If you mean stop clicking on it and it opening a completely blank thing over your inventory, it’s set under initialize within the client class or similar.
[/quote]
I think he means un-null as in use the tab.
In a normal 317, that tab NEVER existed. So you can’t un-null something that wasn’t ever nulled.
Oh, and you’d need to write it there…[/quote]

Not strictly true. The interface tab can be used to show other tabs. Look in Cheezscape 80. I believe this used the corner stone.
